<item>
            <title>[WFLY-2093] No any log generated after changing periodic-rotating-file-handler to size-rotating-file-handler</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-2093</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no any log in the server.log after changing periodic-rotating-file-handler to size-rotating-file-handler.&lt;br/&gt;
The reproduce steps:&lt;br/&gt;
1. remove the part periodic-rotating-file-handler in standalone.xml&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;periodic-rotating-file-handler name=&quot;FILE&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;formatter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;pattern-formatter pattern=&quot;%d&lt;/p&gt;
{HH:mm:ss.SSS}
&lt;p&gt; %-5p &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;%c&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (%t) %s%E%n&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/formatter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;file relative-to=&quot;jboss.server.log.dir&quot; path=&quot;server.log&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;suffix value=&quot;.yyyy-MM-dd&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;append value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/periodic-rotating-file-handler&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
2. add one size-rotating-file-handler&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;size-rotating-file-handler name=&quot;FILE&quot; autoflush=&quot;true&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;formatter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;pattern-formatter pattern=&quot;%d&lt;/p&gt;
{HH:mm:ss,SSS}
&lt;p&gt; %-5p (%c) &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;%t&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; %s%E%n&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/formatter&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;file relative-to=&quot;jboss.server.log.dir&quot; path=&quot;server.log&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;rotate-size value=&quot;500k&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;max-backup-index value=&quot;15&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;append value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/size-rotating-file-handler&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
3. start the jboss server, then you will see there is a warning in the server.log and no any further logs in the server.log.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;13:23:28,205 WARN  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;org.jboss.as.logging&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (Controller Boot Thread) JBAS011511: Replacing handler &apos;FILE&apos; during add operation. Either the handler type or the module name differs from the initial configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The possible fix: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-178&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-178&lt;/a&gt; the code change is in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/wildfly/wildfly/pull/4137&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/wildfly/wildfly/pull/4137&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
and the bugzilla is in EAP6.1.0: &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=918103&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=918103&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But this issue still exists in 6.1.1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Best Regards,&lt;br/&gt;
Vicky&lt;/p&gt;</description>
